  "core_intro7":["Community Manager","13 Years in China","Top 300 Redditor"],
  "core_intro7con":'Community Manager | 13 Years in China | Top 300 Redditor | English/Chinese Social Media Guru |  Mandarin Speaker | Content Creator |  PostNationalist | Dad',
